{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Сделайте переход со старого JS MapsSDK на MapsNativeSDK максимально просто."}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapsNativeSDK"}],"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Переход с JS MapsSDK"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UpdateSdk"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK позволяет получить вам совершенно новый опыт работы с картографической информацией в ваших приложениях в сравнении с "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/maps-mailru\/maps-sdk-ios","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". В этом руководстве будет описан процесс перехода с прошлой версии на новую."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A3%D1%81%D1%82%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%BA%D0%B0-MapsNativeSDK","text":"Установка MapsNativeSDK"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK является не обновлением для JS MapsSDK, а полноценной новой библиотекой, поэтому вы не сможете совершить переход с помощью обновления пакета в SPM, пода в CocoaPods. Вам необходимо произвести установку MapsNativeSDK одним из способов, описанных в статье "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%9F%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D1%85%D0%BE%D0%B4-%D0%BD%D0%B0-MapsNativeSDK","text":"Переход на MapsNativeSDK"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для осуществления перехода на новую версию SDK сделайте следующий шаги:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-1-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-SDK","text":"Шаг 1. Конфигурирование SDK"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"MapsNativeSDK требует произвести конфигурирование SDK до создания первого экземпляра "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"type":"text","text":". Для конфигурирования служит метод "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapsSDKConfigurator\/setup(baseURL:apiKey:diskCachePath:maxCacheSizeBytes:fileTimeoutSec:)"},{"type":"text","text":". Подробнее о его использовании можно прочитать в статье "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/StartUsing","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Предварительное конфигурирование SDK не требовалось","","\/\/ СТАЛО","MapsSDKConfigurator.setup(apiKey: ##API-ключ##)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-2-%D0%9A%D0%BE%D0%BD%D1%84%D0%B8%D0%B3%D1%83%D1%80%D0%B8%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-MapView","text":"Шаг 2. Конфигурирование MapView"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Теперь конфигурацию карты (стартовое положение камеры, стартовый стиль), а так же делегат необходимо передавать в инициализатор объекта ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"text":" (","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/init(frame:configuration:delegate:)","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":").","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","\/\/ Создаем объект карты","let mapView = MapView()","\/\/ Создаем объект конфигурации","let mapConfig = MapViewConfig(","    apiKey: \"##API_KEY##\",","    center: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    zoomLevel: 11,","    style: .automatic",")","\/\/ Устанавливаем конфигурацию","mapView.setup(mapConfig)","\/\/ Устанавливаем делегат","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ СТАЛО","let configuration = MapConfiguration(","    center: Coordinates(","        lng: 35.910974,","        lat: 56.859207","    ),","    zoom: 15,","    predefinedStyle: style,","    selectFeatures: .all,","    cameraMode: .earth",")","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и позже отдельно устанавливаем делегат","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration)","mapView.delegate = self","","\/\/ ИЛИ","\/\/ Передаем конфигурацию и делегат одновременно","mapView = MapView(configuration: configuration, delegate: self)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-3-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D0%BF%D0%B5%D1%80%D0%B5%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%89%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%80%D1%8B","text":"Шаг 3. Изменение методов перемещение камеры"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Для перемещения камеры теперь необходимо обращаться к контроллеру "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/CameraController","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" через свойство ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/camera","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MapView"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для перемещения камеры используется методы группы ","type":"text"},{"code":"flyTo","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" и другие. Подробнее об это читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/CameraMoving","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.flyTo(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), animated: true, duration: 2)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.camera.flyTo(coordinates: .center(Coordinates(lng: 37.427278, lat: 55.756486)), ","                        cameraOptions: .init(bearing: 80, zoom: 12, pitch: 0), ","                        animationOptions: .init(easing: .easeInOut, duration: .max(value: 2)))"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-4-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BC%D0%B5%D1%82%D0%BE%D0%B4%D0%BE%D0%B2-%D1%83%D0%BF%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B2%D0%BB%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D1%8F-%D0%B8%D0%BD%D0%B4%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%BE%D1%80%D0%BE%D0%BC-%D0%BF%D0%BE%D0%BB%D1%8C%D0%B7%D0%BE%D0%B2%D0%B0%D1%82%D0%B5%D0%BB%D1%8F","text":"Шаг 4. Изменение методов управления индикатором пользователя"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для управления индикатором пользователя на карте необходимо обращаться к контроллеру ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UserPointerController","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" через свойство ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapView\/userPointer","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":". Ранее методы управления находились непосредственно в API класса ","type":"text"},{"code":"MapView","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Для отображения и перемещения индикатора пользователя используется группа методов ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setCurrentLocation"},{"text":". Подробнее об это читайте в статье ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/UserPointer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","mapView.setCurrentLocation(Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55), bearing: 0, accuracy: 0)","","\/\/ СТАЛО","mapView.userPointer.setCurrentLocation(","    coordinates: Coordinates(lng: 33, lat: 55),","    bearing: 0,","    accuracy: 0,","    animationDuration: 1)"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"level":3,"type":"heading","anchor":"%D0%A8%D0%B0%D0%B3-5-%D0%98%D0%B7%D0%BC%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B5%D0%BD%D0%B8%D0%B5-%D0%BB%D0%BE%D0%B3%D0%B8%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%BE%D1%82%D0%BA%D0%B8-%D1%81%D0%BE%D0%B1%D1%8B%D1%82%D0%B8%D0%B9-%D0%BA%D0%B0%D1%80%D1%82%D1%8B","text":"Шаг 5. Изменение логики обработки событий карты"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"В MapsNativeSDK сильно переработана система событий, они стали более логичными. Теперь практически для всех типов событий (перемещение камеры, клики по маркерам, события жизненного цикла карты) используется метод "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/MapViewDelegate\/mapView(_:didReceiveEvent:)-7k969","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Более подробно об обработке событий читайте в статье "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapsNativeSDK\/documentation\/MapsNativeSDK\/Lifecycle","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Пример отслеживания событий нажатия на маркер"}],"type":"strong"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["\/\/ БЫЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didSelectMarkerID markerID: String) {}","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: String) {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .clickOnMarker","            \/\/ ...","        }","}","","\/\/ СТАЛО","class MapDelegate: MapViewDelegate{","    func mapView(_ map: MapView, didReceiveEvent event: MapEvent) {","        switch event {","            \/\/ ...","            \/\/ event.type = .platformMarkerDidSelect","            \/\/ или","            \/\/ event.type = .markerDidSelect","            \/\/ ...","        }","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"aside","style":"warning","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"В данный момент MapsNativeSD